---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Контакти">
    <div class="bg-slate-900 py-16 text-white text-center">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6">
                Свържете се с нас
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-300">
                Имате въпроси или искате да помогнете? Не се колебайте да ни
                потърсите.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Phone -->
            <div
                class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 text-center"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 text-orange-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-8 h-8"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Телефон</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
                    Обадете ни се при нужда или за въпроси относно осиновяване.
                </p>
                <a
                    href="tel:0876570311"
                    class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-orange-600 hover:text-orange-700 transition-colors"
                    >087 6570311</a
                >
            </div>

            <!-- Email -->
            <div
                class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 text-center"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 text-orange-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-8 h-8"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
                    Електронна поща
                </h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
                    Пишете ни за общи запитвания и партньорства.
                </p>
                <a
                    href="mailto:animal.hope-varna@gmail.com"
                    class="text-lg font-bold text-orange-600 hover:text-orange-700 transition-colors break-all"
                    >animalhope.varna@gmail.com</a
                >
            </div>

            <!-- Facebook -->
            <div
                class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 text-center"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-8 h-8"
                        fill="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                        <path
                            fill-rule="evenodd"
                            d="M22 12c0-5.523-4.477-10-10-10S2 6.477 2 12c0 4.991 3.657 9.128 8.438 9.878v-6.987h-2.54V12h2.54V9.797c0-2.506 1.492-3.89 3.777-3.89 1.094 0 2.238.195 2.238.195v2.46h-1.26c-1.243 0-1.63.771-1.63 1.562V12h2.773l-.443 2.89h-2.33v6.988C18.343 21.128 22 16.991 22 12z"
                            clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Facebook</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
                    Всички осиновявания и актуални новини се случват тук.
                </p>
                <a
                    href="https://facebook.com/animalhope.varna"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors"
                >
                    Към страницата
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Response time notice -->
        <div class="mt-12 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-2xl p-6 flex gap-4 items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                    d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-amber-800 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <span class="font-bold">Моля, имайте търпение.</span> Организацията се управлява изцяло от доброволци,
                които отделят свободното си време за грижа за животните. Не винаги има човек на
                разположение, който да може да отговори веднага на вашето запитване. Ще се
                свържем с вас при първа възможност — благодарим за разбирането!
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
